snippet.title: CARBOX Reveal Trailer.  Sandbox driving game
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2010100/Carbox

Drive. Build. Share.

Carbox is a Sandbox Driving game
With its easy-to-use and powerful editor, you can let your imagination run wild and create customized maps and races to play and share with other players.
Build your dream city, share it with the community, earn coins and rewards to get more vehicles and content. Drive and compete in an ever-expanding world of custom maps and races!
